<section class="intro-section">
    <div class="title"><span class="caslo-graphique">Welcome</span> to Cities and Beaches</div>
    <p>Proud to offer high-quality, tailor-made tours and holidays - at the best possible price.</p>
</section>
<section class="about-section">
    <img src="@aboutus2" class="lazy" />
    @*<p>
            Cities and Beaches is part of Benz Travel established twenty nine years ago, a pedigree only a few other travel companies can claim and which we feel should give you a sense that you are dealing with both a solid and a secure company which has the requisite financial protection in place through our ATOL licence. We are also members of IATA and hold direct contracts with over 50 international Airlines including Virgin Atlantic, Emirates, Etihad, Qatar and United Airlines to name but a few.
        </p>
        <p>
            Cities and Beaches started off with the ideal of making tailor made holidays where an actual human being would make decisions based on value for money but always with the following question in mind: "Would I go on this Holiday?" You'll find some great ideas on our holiday pages such as our Kerala tour with Private car, elephant ride, backwater stays and meals included, or our top selling city break Rome & Venice where you get two cities for the price of One.
        </p>
        <p>
            We hope you like the website and the holidays we are constatntly putting together.
        </p>*@
    <h4>Our Mission</h4>
    <p>Here at Cities and Beaches we are dedicated to providing you tailor-made tours and holidays that are of exceptionally <strong>high quality</strong> yet still offer <strong>fantastic value</strong>. We’re on-hand to help you find your perfect holiday, one that you will remember for years to come.</p>
    <h4>Personal Service</h4>
    <p>
        Our passionate and highly-skilled team build trusted relationships with customers, and work hard to maintain a connection with you long past the day you return from your trip. We are also focused on ensuring that when you choose Cities and Beaches that you receive the highest standard of <strong>customer care</strong>. We know that it’s the little things that make the difference and we believe your holiday should be nothing short of incredible.
    </p>
    <h4>Location Experts</h4>
    <p>
        As well a caring customer services team, we also have <strong>location experts</strong> who curate our tours, creating extra special itineraries due to their inside knowledge. Our carefully crafted packages, which include transfers, excursions and many entrance fees in the price, have been designed to ensure you have an exceptional, carefree experience. We also offer you the chance to explore at your own pace and do your own thing, as we know many customers enjoy a balance of pre-arranged excursions and free time.
    </p>
    <h4>Handpicked Hotels</h4>
    <p>
        The wonderful hotels across all our getaways have been handpicked and checked on <strong>TripAdvisor</strong> for quality assurance, before being included in the itinerary. We believe that accommodation should be one of the many highlights of your trip, which is why we work hard to ensure our hotels exceed your expectations. We even have a collection of all-inclusive holidays, where the emphasis is firmly on relaxation and enjoying the resort facilities.
    </p>
    <h4>Our Background</h4>
    <p>
        At Cities and Beaches we offer tours and holidays to <strong>55 destinations</strong>. Some of our most popular adventures include our <strong>Golden Triangle Tour</strong> in India and our <strong>Cambodia and Vietnam tour</strong>. We also offer a wide range of <strong>package holidays</strong> and <strong>city breaks</strong> with <strong>Italy</strong> our top-selling European destination. We hold <strong>ATOL and PTS</strong> so you can book your holiday safe in the knowledge you are financially protected.
    </p>

    <h4>Why Book with Us? </h4>
    <p>
        As well as our focus on <strong>quality, value</strong> and exceptional <strong>customer service</strong> our well-travelled, passionate team also have the <strong>travel expertise</strong> to ensure that when you book with us you can expect a wonderful time. Our location experts have multiple contracts with top international airlines including Virgin Atlantic, Emirates, Etihad and Qatar and through these contracts we are able to offer you competitive fares on flights from <strong>all UK airports</strong> as part of our tours and holidays. It’s contracts like these that allow us to maintain our high quality but still offer you affordable packages.
    </p>
    <p> When you book with Citrus, you can expect top quality at exceptional value. Start your journey with Cities and Beaches today…</p>
</section>
