                </div>
                <p>
                    The booking process was great.  Mel went the extra mile to find me a suitable holiday at the cheapest price.  Very impressed. The holiday itself, brilliant for someone like me.  Loads packed into the inclusive itinerary.  A great break. This was the Kerala 9 days tour with resort at the end.
