                <p>
                    Wow Citrus what a holiday!  We were so looking forward to this trip and visiting India and we were not disappointed.   You were recommended to us by our friends and we would certainly recommend you further.  From the initial booking with Citrus, right through to the flight home, everything went to plan and generally exceeded our expectations.  We met a great bunch of people on the trip and it was great to meet up at the end of the day over dinner to share the day. Can't wait to book our next trip!
