                <div class="testimonial-title">
                    Still in a daze!
                </div>
                <p>
                    I have just returned from the Southern India tour and I am still in a bit of a daze as it was so magical. I can’t believe all of the things that we did in those 15 days.  The hotel accommodation and food was of a high standard and none of us suffered any problems throughout the whole tour. The overnight stay in the boat was a particular highlight - the food in particular was yummy. Overall an amazing tour - unbelievable value for money and thoroughly recommended.
