            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-wrapper">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <div class="testimonial-title">
                    Couldn't have asked for better service.  
                </div>
                <p>
                    Couldn't have asked for better service.  I booked the holiday with Citrus on a whim and my trip entailed a full tour of Sri Lanka and then a rest stay at the Maldives.  I paid in full on booking and to be honest, was a little apprehensive about the company as I heard nothing then until close to departure, however.  The attacks on Sri Lanka occurred three days before we were due to depart the UK and although I never actually got to speak to a person, as all requests were dealt with via email, the representatives at Citrus went above and beyond to change all the flight and hotel stay to the Maldives with no further coat apart from the £6 a day environment tax for going direct to the Maldives.  Couldn't recommend them enough.  No issues. Very happy
                </p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    ~ Mrs Natalie Thomas
                    <span class="testimonial-date">, May 11th 2019</span>
                </div>
                <img src="../../assets/img/aboutus/quotation-marks.svg" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-wrapper">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <div class="testimonial-title">
                    Used them regularly over the last five years
                </div>
                <p>
                    Used them regularly over the last five years.easy to deal with mixture of e mails and phone calls made booking easy.still feels like a personal service with modern methods. Great value,you get what it says on the tin. Last trip was the Southern India Explorer.good hotels, great itinerary,personal chauffeur etc Our driver helped make the trip great.He looked after us for 10 days always well turned out ,engaging and knowledgeable . I regularly recommend Citrus to our friends.
                </p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    ~ Christopher Rees
                    <span class="testimonial-date">, May 1st 2019</span>
                </div>
                <img src="../../assets/img/aboutus/quotation-marks.svg" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-wrapper">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <div class="testimonial-title">
                    We had an excellent trip to Cuba.
                </div>
                <p>
                    We had an excellent trip to Cuba booked through Cities and Beaches. Flights, transfers and hotel bookings and an included excursion all went according to plan. If you want a company to just make all the arrangements for you and to e-mail the vouchers/tickets to you just before travel, and at a reasonable price, then Citrus is a good choice. You do need to check and obtain what visa or other documentation that you might need yourself, but this is easily checked on the UK foreign office travel advice website.
                </p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    ~ Carole Kerrigan
                    <span class="testimonial-date">, June 16th 2019</span>
                </div>
                <img src="../../assets/img/aboutus/quotation-marks.svg" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-wrapper">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <div class="testimonial-title">
                    The best holiday I can remember!  
                </div>
                <p>
                    The best holiday I can remember!  All arrangements were carried out in an efficient manner.  We were met as per schedule with all the guides/agents being courteous, punctual and informative. Also ''Ravi'' on your bookings team was very helpful, and nothing was too much trouble for him to ensure our flights, hotels and schedule were just as required.  You can be assured that we will book further holidays with you, and will happily recommend Citrus to our friends and colleagues.  Thank you! Regards, Adrian and Kim Brant
                </p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    ~ Adrian Brant
                    <span class="testimonial-date">, Nov 21st 2018</span>
                </div>
                <img src="../../assets/img/aboutus/quotation-marks.svg" />
